************************************************************************

			 Ocaml FFTW interface

************************************************************************

Requirements
------------

Ocaml > 3.04.

The FFTW library version 2, including the development files.  You can
download it from "http://www.fftw.org/".  On Debian, install the
"fftw-dev" package.

Compilation
-----------

Type 

- "make" to compile the library;

- "make install" to install it (requires ocamlfind).
